contents: pt. 1. Smithsonian Institution. Treasury Department. Tariff Commission. Veterans Administration. Veterans Bureau. Vocational Education Board (5 v.) -- pt. 2. Commerce Department (6 v.) -- pt. 3. War Department, War Trade Board (5 v.) -- pt. 4. Interior Department (4 v.) -- pt. 5. Agriculture Department (6 v.) -- pt. 6. Library of Congress. Mediation Board. Mediation and Conciliation Board. Navy Department. National Academy of Sciences. National Capital Parks and Planning Commission. President of U.S. State Department. Shipping Board. Philippine Government War Department [...] and other agencies (4 v.).
lds60: Also serves as an index to the CIS microfiche collection entitled: U.S. executive branch documents, 1910-1932.

Part 1 consists of 5 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, SI.1 to T57.7 [2] Reference bibliography, TC1.1 to VE1.15 [3] Index by subjects and names, A-L [4] Index by subjects and names, M-Z [5] Supplementary indexes.

Part 2 consists of 6 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, C1.1 to C17.1 [2] Reference bibliography, C18.1 to C26.2 [3] Index by subjects and names, A-E [4] Index by subjects and names, F-M [5] Index by subjects and names, N-Z [6] Supplementary indexes.

Part 3 consists of 5 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, W1.1 to W29.7 [2] Reference bibliography, W30.1 to W46.2, W53.1 to WT5.2 [3] Index by subjects and names, A-L [4] Index by subjects and names, M-Z [5] Supplementary indexes.
Part 4 consists of 4 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, I1.1 to L14.4 [2] Index by subjects and names, A-L [3] Index by subjects and names, K-Z [4] Supplementary indexes.

Part 5 consists of 6 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, A1.1 to A9.16 [2] Reference bibliography, A10.1 to A53.13 [3] Index by subjects and names, A-E [4] Index by subjects and names, F-N [5] Index by subjects and names, O-Z [6] Supplementary indexes.
Part 6 consists of 4 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, LC1.1 to NH1.7 [2] Index by subjects and names, A-M [3] Index by subjects and names, N-Z [4] Supplementary indexes.
Part 7 consists of 4 unnumbered volumes with titles: [1] Reference bibliography, AR1.6 to W49.55 [2] Index by subjects and names, A-K [3] Index by subjects and names, L-Z [4] Supplementary indexes.
